testCase.name: ResponsiveService constructor should initialize breakpointObserver with all breakpoints
ResponsiveService constructor should update breakpointState when breakpointObserver emits
ResponsiveService isMobile should return true when isXSmall is true
ResponsiveService isMobile should return false when isXSmall is false
ResponsiveService isTablet should return true when isSmall is true
ResponsiveService isTablet should return true when isMedium is true
ResponsiveService isTablet should return false when neither isSmall nor isMedium is true
ResponsiveService isDesktop should return true when isLarge is true
ResponsiveService isDesktop should return true when isXLarge is true
ResponsiveService isDesktop should return false when neither isLarge nor isXLarge is true
ResponsiveService currentBreakpoint should return "xsmall" when isXSmall is true
ResponsiveService currentBreakpoint should return "small" when isSmall is true
ResponsiveService currentBreakpoint should return "medium" when isMedium is true
ResponsiveService currentBreakpoint should return "large" when isLarge is true
ResponsiveService currentBreakpoint should return "xlarge" when isXLarge is true or no other breakpoint is active
